[Leon] There's nothing special here. Just some
small talk, you know.

[Skeleton Head] You're cute today too. It doesn't
matter that you're male.
[Chachamaru] Meow...
[Masamune] Hey, stop it.
[Skeleton Head] Just kidding.
[Chachamaru] Meow...
[Masamune] What is it!

[Skeleton Head] A magic circle! Can Chachamaru use
magic?
[Leon] I've never heard of a cat like that before.

[Leon] Chachamaru is just a cat that we keep in
the Howard Dormitory. It can't use magic or
anything.
[Masamune] Then, what was that just now...

[Skeleton Head] I don't know, but I'll chase after
them anyway.

【Masamune】 I wonder what this room is. Is it just
an empty room...?

【Skeleton Head】 Hey, Masamune. Did you hear the
rumors and come here?

【Masamune】 Oh, it's you guys again... What kind of
rumor is it this time? If it's about cute
monsters, spare me.
【Skeleton Head】 No, no. It's a much better rumor.

【Skeleton Head】 Apparently, there is a secret
passage that connects the men's dormitory and the
women's dormitory in Howard House.
【Masamune】 What...?

【Skeleton Head】 I heard that students made a
secret passage in the past.

【Skeleton Head】 If you find it, you'll be able to
freely peek into the daily lives of the girls.
【Masamune】 ...Isn't that just a crime?

【Tommy】 I also tried to stop them from doing that,
but they didn't listen.

【Skeleton Head】 Of course! Peeking into the girls'
room is a man's romance, isn't it!
【Masamune】 Just a pervert.

【Masamune】 I have no intention of getting involved
in a crime.

【Leon】 I agree. But it's still intriguing, isn't
it?
【Leon】 Is there really such a passage?
【Masamune】 That is certainly...

【Leon】 Even Tommy, who knows a lot about secret
passages, has no idea of its existence.

【Tommy】 If something like that exists, the
professor would crush it immediately.
【Masamune】 Isn't that the case?
【Skeleton Head】 I have it!

【Skeleton Head】 Everyone wants to peek into the
girls' dormitory.

【Skeleton Head】 In this long-standing academy,
there's no way nobody has done it.
【Skeleton Head】 There must be a genius.
【Masamune】 Even perverts...

【Masamune】 Well, let's just search for it. If it
exists, we can just tell the professor.
【Skeleton Head】 Don't say that!

【Leon】 For now, this room seems suspicious. It's
been vacant for a while.

【Leon】 When you move up to the upper division, you
get to choose a new room, but this one has never
been popular.

【Leon】 I think it's fine because it's a corner
room.

【Masamune】 So even Leon didn't choose this room,
huh?
【Leon】 Ah, yeah. I don't remember why anymore.
【Skeleton Head】 Let's search for it anyway.
